Original Ghostbuster, Ernie Hudson, Only Earned $370 Out Of His First $10,000 Hollywood Paycheck

40 years after the original, Hudson is back in 'Ghostbusters: Frozen Empire.' He shared how he feels about his digital likeness being used long after he's gone.
